These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, siglo, baccarat, aristoff, swisher, alhambra, bluemaster
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, baking, gardening, rock-climbing, reading, woodworking
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the dutch##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the swisher-smoker##1
12. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the german##1
16. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
17. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
